{"type": "excalidraw", "version": 2, "source": "excalidraw-diagram-skill", "elements": [{"type": "rectangle", "id": "darkbg", "x": -4000, "y": -3000, "width": 10000, "height": 7500, "backgroundColor": "#1e1e2e", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "transparent", "strokeWidth": 0, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100}, {"type": "text", "id": "title1", "x": 20, "y": 10, "width": 728, "height": 28, "text": "#### React 18의 Automatic Batching", "fontSize": 20, "strokeColor": "#e5e5e5", "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "opacity": 100}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "box2", "x": 20, "y": 45, "width": 728.5, "height": 646, "backgroundColor": "#1e3a5f", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#4a9eed", "strokeWidth": 2, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "roundness": {"type": 3}}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt3", "x": 35, "y": 60, "width": 698, "height": 616, "text": "React 17까지는 이벤트 핸들러 안에서만 Batching이 동작했다. React 18부터는 **모든 상황에서** 자동으로 Batching된다.\n```jsx\nfunction AsyncBatching() {\nconst [count, setCount] = useState(0);\nconst [flag, setFlag] = useState(false);\nconst handleClick = () => {\n//  이벤트 핸들러\n// React 17 ✅, React 18 ✅ → 항상 Batching됨\nsetCount((c) => c + 1);\nsetFlag((f) => !f);\n// → 1번의 렌더링\n//  Promise 콜백\nfetch(\"/api/data\").then(() => {\nsetCount((c) => c + 1);\nsetFlag((f) => !f);\n// React 17: 2번의 렌더링 ❌\n// React 18: 1번의 렌더링 ✅ (Automatic Batching)\n});\n//  setTimeout\nsetTimeout(() => {\nsetCount((c) => c + 1);\nsetFlag((f) => !f);\n// React 17: 2번의 렌더링 ❌\n// React 18: 1번의 렌더링 ✅ (Automatic Batching)\n}, 1000);\n};\nreturn <button onClick={handleClick}>{count}</button>;\n}", "fontSize": 14, "strokeColor": "#e5e5e5", "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "middle", "opacity": 100, "containerId": "box2"}], "appState": {"viewBackgroundColor": "#1e1e2e"}}